description: This week it's Tyler Saint & Blake Daniels vs Sebastian Keys & Emanuel in an epic tag team match in front of a live audience! The line was down the block to get into this standing room only event. This was without a doubt our most extreme and most successful Live Naked Kombat Tag Team Match to date! The guys really brought it on for the screaming crowd and the action does not stop. With the action over and the winners revealed, the final sex round turns out to be as intense as the wrestling. Don't believe it? See for yourself. And look for some unexpected surprises along the way.
title: Tyler Saint & Blake Daniels vs Sebastian Keys & Emanuel
